</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_186" id="91v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_186_r2l1">Der Stat cʒu Tauſt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Andres Hüts
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l3"><expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / Darümb <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> wirtin </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l4">beſant / vnd cʒurede geſacʒt /
                            <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> derſelb Jr wirte cʒu der cʒeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l5">niht anheim iſt / vnd alſo hat ſıe vns
                                <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / daʒ ſıe cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l9">mal von der ſache <add><ab facs="#facs_186_line_1575889116285_1141"><expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> Jr vns
                                        <expan>geſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> habt </ab></add> nihts
                        wiſſe / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Jr wirte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> herheim kümt / So
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir Jn <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l11">gern cʒurede ſecʒen / vnd waʒ Er vns
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> darüber
                            <expan>cʒuantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l12">gibt / iſt <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> der vns von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> daran mant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l13">ſo <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir das ewr
                        freuntſchaft <add><ab facs="#facs_186_line_1575889265283_1161"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
</ab></add> wiſſen laſſen / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l15"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Ocuıl </del> Oculi / Anno ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_186" id="91v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Taust </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Andres Hüts,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>; darümb
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> wirtin besant und czurede gesaczt,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> derselb ir wirte czu der czeit niht
                        anheim ist, und also hat sie uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz sie
                        czu mal von der sache, <add><expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> ir uns
                                    <expan>ges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> habt</add>, nihts wisse;
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ir wirte,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, herheim kümt, so
                            <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen gern czurede seczen und waz er uns
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> darüber
                            <expan>czuantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> gibt, ist
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan>, der uns von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> daran mant, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir das ewr freuntschaft
                            <add><expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan></add> wissen lassen;
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> oculi anno ix<hi rend="sup">no</hi>.</ab>
</div>
